{
  "stem": "2533.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then he went into an office, and he saw blood on-- on-- on a door or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that German was lying under the-- the desk, dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then went the alarms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the shooting started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And some of the boys and the men were impatient.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They wanted to climb over the barbed wire, and they got shocked on there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then the boys started to cut the wire through so we could run.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the shooting-- the most damage were done from the towers where the Ukraine guards were, because the Germans had only rifles or pistols.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the machine guns were up top in the towers, and there were four towers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So what the machine--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was 10 minutes before when that tragedy happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And maybe we would have got out a lot, lot more of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe not all, but we would have-- not that many would have been killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I started running.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't far away from that opening they made in the fences.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on the way, there was somewhere a bush, because not only that, but from the camp to the forest, there was more than a kilometer clearing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was even some logs were lying there, and we had to jump over the logs and duck-- you know, not the shooting, just to the opposite direction of the shooting.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then my little bag with that little bit of sugar I had got caught on a branch, and there wasn't time to untangle it, so I just let it go.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I stopped running in the forest, turned around-- there were a lot, a lot of us, hundreds, I should say-- there was only three of us.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
